Vego Avocado Ritz: (4 persons = half avo p.p.)

* 200g stilton cheese
* 100g walnuts, coarsely chopped
* 1 egg
* 50g breadcrumbs
* 100ml double cream
* 2 medium avocado

== Method == 
#  preheat the oven to 180C/gas 
# Mix the Stilton and walnuts together in a bowl.
#  Add the egg and breadcrumbs and stir to combine.
#  Add the cream and mix well.
#  Cut the avocados in half and remove the stone.
#  Divide the Stilton mixture evenly between the avocados. Bake for 15-20 minutes.
